p3opensteer
***********

p3opensteer is project which integrates (some functionality of) OpenSteer
library (http://opensteer.sourceforge.net/) into Panda3d game engine 
(https://www.panda3d.org) as a extension module.

OpenSteer is a C++ library to help construct "steering behaviors" for 
autonomous characters in games and animation. 

p3opensteer are currently developed and tested on GNU/Linux (Debian 8 - 
jessie) platform. Since there is no platform specific code, it should builds 
and run successfully on other platforms supported by Panda3d.  

p3opensteer is a GPL v3 licensed open source project. A copy of the GNU 
General Public License is reported into COPYING file. 
See also <http://www.gnu.org/licenses/>.

